</b></p>
<p><b>policies, and programmes; and ensure the enjoyment on an equal footing within 
</b></p>
<p><b>all provinces and territories of the rights set forth in the International 
</b></p>
<p><b>Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination (ICERD), 
