xenophobia and related intolerance (Senegal); </b></p>


<p>128.41.<b> Make further efforts in the fight against all forms of discrimination 
and intolerance (Viet Nam); 
</b></p>
<p>128.42.<b> Intensify its efforts to fight against all forms of racism, racial 
discrimination, xenophobia and related intolerance, including Islamophobia 
</b></p>
<p><b>(Algeria); 
</b></p>
<p>128.43.<b> Take measures to prohibit targeting, profiling and harassment of 
